BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 597.48 Td (Dear Delegates,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 577.90 Td (It is with great pleasure that we welcome you to UN Women \(UN Women\) at MUNBOLDT 2027.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 563.40 Td (Over the course of this conference, you will be asked to step into the shoes of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 548.90 Td (representatives entrusted with shaping real solutions to one of today's most pressing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 534.40 Td (global challenges: Advancing Gender Equality and Women's Economic Empowerment in Fragile) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 519.90 Td (and Conflict-Affected Settings.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 500.33 Td (This background guide is meant to give you a starting point for your research — it is not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 485.83 Td (a substitute for your own investigation. We encourage you to read widely, consult primary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 471.33 Td (sources whenever possible, and arrive at committee ready to defend your delegation's) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 456.83 Td (position with evidence and conviction.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 437.25 Td (Debate in UN Women can move quickly, and the issues you will discuss do not have easy) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 422.75 Td (answers. We expect creativity, respectful disagreement, and a genuine willingness to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 408.25 Td (listen to perspectives different from your own. Diplomacy is not about winning an) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 393.75 Td (argument; it is about finding workable solutions that a diverse group of stakeholders can) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 379.25 Td (stand behind.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 359.68 Td (We look forward to seeing the resolutions, communiqués, and ideas you bring to the table.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 345.18 Td (Should any questions arise before or during the conference, please do not hesitate to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 330.68 Td (reach out to the dais.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 311.10 Td (Sincerely,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 291.53 Td (The UN Women Dais — MUNBOLDT 2027) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 72 263.98 Td (II. Introduction to the Committee) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 239.33 Td (UN Women is the United Nations entity dedicated to gender equality and the empowerment of) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 224.83 Td (women. It supports Member States in setting global standards for achieving gender) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 210.33 Td (equality and works alongside governments and civil society to design the laws, policies,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 195.83 Td (programmes, and services needed to put those standards into practice.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 176.25 Td (As you prepare for UN Women, take time to understand not only what this body can formally) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 161.75 Td (decide, but also how it operates in practice: how proposals move from an idea to a vote,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 147.25 Td (what level of consensus is realistically required, and what happens after a decision is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 132.75 Td (adopted. Understanding these mechanics will make your strategy — and your speeches — far) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.5 Tf 72 118.25 Td (more convincing.) Tj ET
BT /F2 13 Tf 72 90.70 Td (III. Background and History of the Topic) Tj ET
